# 🌸 PCOS Dashboard

A comprehensive, role-based web application built with Streamlit and MariaDB to help patients, healthcare professionals, and 
administrators track, monitor, and analyze Polycystic Ovary Syndrome (PCOS) symptoms and risk factors using Machine Learning.

## ✨ Key Features

This platform is divided into three distinct, secure portals based on the user's role:

 👤 For Patients (Role 1):
     Daily Journal: Log symptoms, lifestyle changes, and hormonal cycles.
     ML Analysis: Get AI-driven insights and risk predictions based on questionnaire data.
     Personalized Resources: Receive curated educational content tailored to specific health needs.
 🩺 For Healthcare Professionals (Role 2):
     Patient Connection: Securely link with patients using their email.
     Health Monitoring: View patient journals, questionnaire results, and ML risk assessments in real-time.
 ⚙️ For Administrators (Role 3):
     System Analytics: Monitor platform health, user growth, and overall ML model confidence.
     User Management: Approve, edit, or remove users and export database backups.

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

 Frontend: Streamlit, HTML/CSS (Custom UI Components)
 Backend: Python 3
 Database: MariaDB (SQL)
 Machine Learning: Scikit-Learn, XGBoost, Imbalanced-Learn
 Data Visualization: Pandas, Plotly, Matplotlib

---

## 📂 Project Structure

```text
pcos_dashboard/
├── .env                    # Environment variables 
├── .streamlit/ 
│   ├── secrets.toml     
│   └── config.toml  
│
├── README.md               # Project documentation
└── src/                      
    ├── app.py              # Application Entry Point (Login & Signup)
    ├── ml.py               # Machine Learning models and pipelines
    ├── requirements.txt    # Python dependencies  
    │
    ├── assets/             # Static assets
    │   └── style.css       # Global custom UI styling
    │
    ├── database/           # Database Layer
    │   ├── connection.py   # MariaDB connection handler
    │   └── queries.py      # Prepared SQL queries
    │
    ├── utils/              # Helper Functions
    │   ├── auth_tools.py   # Session state, password hashing, validation
    │   ├── email_tool.py   # OTP and notification emails
    │   ├── questions.py    # questionaire questions
    │   └── ui_helpers.py   # CSS loaders and repeated UI logic
    │
    ├── components/         # Reusable UI Blocks
    │   ├── charts.py       # Plotly chart generators
    │   ├── metrics.py      # KPI metric cards
    │   ├── sidebar.py      # Role-based navigation
    │   └── header.py       # App header / branding
    │
    └── pages/              # Streamlit Application Pages
        ├── 01_profile.py   
        ├── 02_dashboard.py 
        ├── 03_questionnaire.py 
        ├── 04_resources.py 
        │
        ├── 11_user_journal.py            # Patient Tools
        ├── 12_user_daily_quest.py 
        ├── 13_user_personal_resources.py 
        │
        ├── 21_pro_connect.py             # Professional Tools
        ├── 22_pro_monitor.py 
        ├── 23_pro_details.py 
        │
        ├── 31_admin_dashboard.py         # Admin Tools
        └── 32_user_management.py